{"tid":2178660,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"一人一個叫老細收皮既方法","createTime":"2020-08-28T13:44:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-29T12:25:01.000Z","uid":192581,"like":2,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"b598f5541f430bf1fdd35508f9c16f8168fac1d6","tid":2178660,"uid":192581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T13:44:55.000Z","msg":"FG文員 老細逼人做到三四點又無補水 成日話經濟差 唔做勤力啲就炒 又吹到自己有幾叻 依家啲後生好無用<br />\n<br />\n有無曲線辦法叫佢收皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n利申：未搵到工 好難辭職 但想佢收皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3297667ae40f1b825997dc2762165c1edcb50bfd","tid":2178660,"uid":192581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T13:46:02.000Z","msg":"求集思廣益<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9eed55a8c343eb180cb9698572122516c886d34d","tid":2178660,"uid":288586,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T13:54:05.000Z","msg":"叫佢收皮"},{"pid":"a24e64dc983790770941b85769420f5ca4e0bc0c","tid":2178660,"uid":273014,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T13:55:42.000Z","msg":"明明係奴性重，但就講到係優點話自己勤力、捱得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9af640b8a62c553ebd5bf240447a34f342540fcb","tid":2178660,"uid":273014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a24e64dc983790770941b85769420f5ca4e0bc0c","tid":2178660,"uid":273014,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T13:55:42.000Z","msg":"明明係奴性重，但就講到係優點話自己勤力、捱得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T13:56:33.000Z","msg":"我講緊你老細"},{"pid":"7836165b6465cf08109dc06c9a57550e8c597095","tid":2178660,"uid":177089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T13:57:18.000Z","msg":"wts佢收皮"},{"pid":"0a93778535ac098c2dada68864c0a3f64d77f95c","tid":2178660,"uid":283991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T13:58:27.000Z","msg":"老細吹到自己好撚勁，即係點屌佢都唔會收皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最好就糧照出，日日準時放工，佢屌你果陣你就整D屎佢嘆，佢咁撚把炮叫佢自己做埋佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"918e49202ac393dff9e7d76643be3494d13c91cc","tid":2178660,"uid":191453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T13:59:12.000Z","msg":"我發夢成日夢到我會落藥整暈佢<br />\n再用美工刀一刀一刀切佢d皮落嚟<br />\n再放入我精皮手提包入面<br />\n最後輕輕的離去 只收走佢厚厚的臉皮"},{"pid":"527d944649ea7268485dee889cfb4c74d5a94fee","tid":2178660,"uid":358948,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T14:05:22.000Z","msg":"五點九執定野，一到六點，就走人。<br />\n佢話仲有野做，你就好堅定咁同佢講唔得閒，有野做。<br />\n如果佢好無恥咁問你有咩做。堅定啲話有野做.有野做.有野做。<br />\n千祈唔好多作解釋，因為按時收工，係唔需要解釋嘅。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果佢真係因為咁而炒你，係因為你廢，唔ot做奴隸就無利用價值。如果咁嘅情況，我情願唔做。加油！唔好做奴隸。<br />\n無錢嘅OT係做爛市，自貶身價。<br />\n同埋唔好見你唔收工，你就唔敢收工。<br />\n佢地戇鳩係佢地嘅事！<br />\n睇一睇僱佣合約，對比一下啲印佣菲佣<br />\n再望望窗外面，呢度係香港。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n無良僱主唔可以縱容！<br />\n而家你唔係每日賺九位數嘅收入！"},{"pid":"a122bc434bc961e39533f97725f5f8ca88cd0143","tid":2178660,"uid":192581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9af640b8a62c553ebd5bf240447a34f342540fcb","tid":2178660,"uid":273014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a24e64dc983790770941b85769420f5ca4e0bc0c","tid":2178660,"uid":273014,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T13:55:42.000Z","msg":"明明係奴性重，但就講到係優點話自己勤力、捱得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T13:56:33.000Z","msg":"我講緊你老細"},"